### Description

It's as if the incremental compilation isn't working properly for my setup. 

I've debugged it a bit, and I can see that when following the instructions in this [comment](https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/issues/8259#issue-269908550) upon changing the `main.ts` with `console.log(1)` all my lazy loaded routes are being marked as `physicallyChangedTsFiles ` when putting a debug break on [L189](https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/addd7f6249d54e258109f139fad1db0d0250352c/packages/compiler-cli/src/ngtsc/incremental/src/incremental.ts#L189) in incremental.ts in `@angular/compiler-cli`.

Not sure if the above is intended, but it's something that I noticed.

